Having got up, Matic chased down Barnes and pushed him over in anger – earning himself a straight red card.

The 26-year-old will miss Sunday’s final against Tottenham as well as Premier League games against West Ham and Southampton – unless he appeals the decision and it is upheld.

Barnes was not booked for the incident and was lucky to escape a yellow for a first-half kick on Ivanovic as he jumped to head a ball. 

